        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "number": "1",
        "title": "It Actually Matches Your Skin Tone — Every Time",
        "body_text": "<p>Most foundations give you a shade range and wish you luck. And if your undertone doesn't cooperate? You're left looking too orange, too pink, or just off.</p><p>Tone-adapting foundation works differently. The formula reacts to your skin's own pH and adapts to your exact tone — light, medium, or deep — without guessing. No more buying three shades hoping one of them works.</p>",
        "link_text": "Learn more",
