      "type": "bl-reason-item",
      "name": "BL - Reason Item",
      "settings": {
        "section_id": "",
        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "number": "2",
        "title": "No More Cakey, Heavy Finish",
        "body_text": "<p>Traditional foundations sit on top of your skin. By midday they've settled, creased, and somehow made everything you were trying to conceal more visible.</p><p>Tone-adapting formula melts in rather than piling on. The result is a second-skin finish that looks clean and natural — not like you're wearing a mask, but like you just happen to have really good skin.</p>",
        "link_text": "learn more",
        "link_type": "anchor",
        "link_anchor": "offer",
