      "name": "BL - Reason Item",
      "settings": {
        "section_id": "",
        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "number": "3",
        "title": "Your Skin Shows Through — In a Good Way",
        "body_text": "<p>Mature skin has character. Freckles. History. And heavy coverage that completely buries it tends to look exactly like what it is — heavy coverage.</p><p>Tone-adapting foundation enhances rather than conceals. You still look like you — just more even, more polished, more radiant. The kind of finish where people ask if you've been on vacation, not what foundation you're wearing.</p>",
        "link_text": "learn more",
        "link_type": "anchor",
        "link_anchor": "offer",
        "link_url": "",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_Reasons_Why_Image_-_00004.webp",
