    "bl_reason_item_NeYbkD": {
      "type": "bl-reason-item",
      "name": "BL - Reason Item",
      "settings": {
        "section_id": "",
        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "number": "4",
        "title": "It Lasts All Day Without Touch-Ups",
        "body_text": "<p>Foundation that fades, patches, or oxidizes by noon is one of the most common complaints from women with mature skin. You spend 20 minutes getting ready and it's gone before lunch.</p><p>Because tone-adapting technology bonds with your skin rather than sitting on top of it, it stays put. Morning through evening. No midday touch-ups, no patchiness, no wondering why you bothered.</p>",
        "link_text": "learn more",
        "link_type": "anchor",
