      "name": "BL - Reason Item",
      "settings": {
        "section_id": "",
        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "number": "5",
        "title": "It Was Designed for Mature Skin — Not as an Afterthought",
        "body_text": "<p>Most foundations are built for 25-year-old skin and then marketed to everyone else. The formulas aren't designed for the way mature skin actually behaves — drier, more sensitive, more nuanced in tone.</p><p>Vera Lane Tone Adapting Foundation was built from the ground up for skin like yours. Hyaluronic acid, niacinamide, vitamin E, and squalane — skincare and foundation in one step. That's the difference.</p>",
